long_description: i'm vivienne, a passionate makeup artist who believes that beauty comes in all forms, shades, and styles. whether you're prepping for a big event, a photo shoot, or simply want to treat yourself to a little extra glow, i'm here to help you feel confident, empowered, and absolutely stunning. i offer a range of services, from flawless everyday looks to bold, artistic creations, all tailored to your unique features and preferences. wedding makeup "makeup is for everyone.". while you'll see lots of brides on my socials, i truly believe makeup is for all people — whether you're the bride, groom, marrier, or anyone else involved in your special day. need an extra pair of hands. someone to hype you up. on your wedding day, there's no "one-size-fits-all" look — your makeup should make you feel like yourself, love a red lip, lets do it, rainbow eyes, absolutely, all the glitter, talk to me goose. i offer personalized makeup lessons where we work together to master techniques that suit your face, style, and lifestyle.
